{"tid":870933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙里疑似撩鼻屎後抹落摩連奴身上！摩帥仍笑嘻嘻！","createTime":"2018-10-21T13:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T14:19:03.000Z","uid":53121,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"280ac571200c5aa1948ca4da42c4122575214d08","tid":870933,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"車路士主場和曼聯 2-2的比賽，終場前摩連奴在場邊被車路士助教挑釁暴跳如雷比 比賽更吸引眼球。賽后摩連奴感謝車路士主教練沙里已經幫助解決了問題，但有車路士球迷爆料，沙里也有不尊重摩連奴的舉動。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2018/10/21/19783dedb7ca4985aaddbf91282ce21f.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F19783dedb7ca4985aaddbf91282ce21f.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=b1553c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摩連奴在賽後讚揚了沙里的處理，他說：&ldquo;和沙里助教之間發生的事情？沙里是第一個向我走來並且說他會解決的人，助教已經向我道歉了，我告訴他忘記這一切吧，我在生涯裡也犯過很多錯。&rdquo;但摩連奴和沙里交談時，可能沒有註意到一個細節。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2018/10/21/0b886ba585434fe2aeebcbd6692be5af.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F0b886ba585434fe2aeebcbd6692be5af.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=e7fe3d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有一名在事發地點邊上的球迷爆料說，沙里在和摩連奴交談前，先挖了挖自己的鼻子，疑似掏出了鼻屎，然後用挖鼻子的手&ldquo;親切&rdquo;地撫摸著摩連奴的後背。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2018/10/21/9d3afd6ab07b4c48a9c3c8f8a8576133.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F9d3afd6ab07b4c48a9c3c8f8a8576133.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=1c3156f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於沙里的舉動，有兩名車路士球迷為此留言，一個說：沙里挖出了鼻屎並放在了摩連奴身上，實在有點沒法喜愛沙里，還一個說：我的天，沙里挖出了鼻屎，然後把它擦在了摩連奴的外套上。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2018/10/21/03d13e0bd411411b9b53cec717813259.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F03d13e0bd411411b9b53cec717813259.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=7ab536fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當今足壇最著名、最喜歡撩鼻屎的是德國主教練路夫，他不僅有撩鼻屎自己吃的鏡頭，還有撩鼻屎後立刻和C朗握手的鏡頭。自從路夫被拍到撩鼻屎後，他就經常被攝影機重點關照，沙里在爆出撩鼻屎後，估計以後也會被攝影機重點關照，沙里需要更注意自己的行為。"},{"pid":"ef37d07e194fe7ddc302794ab717ddad3850853f","tid":870933,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:48:53.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"682cce3778e66c66f3077c18a58ea06f514911e3","tid":870933,"uid":3454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"唔兜口兜面噴煙咪算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0798f170488a4652f8c69380434200b695d9f385","tid":870933,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"Low likes it."},{"pid":"a89a15fd52592a3dc8c237732a8e816dbfea8502","tid":870933,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0798f170488a4652f8c69380434200b695d9f385","tid":870933,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"Low likes it."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"金盈"},{"pid":"2b3144498393e29b8c77b4513da0e4838304e125","tid":870933,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a89a15fd52592a3dc8c237732a8e816dbfea8502","tid":870933,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0798f170488a4652f8c69380434200b695d9f385","tid":870933,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"Low likes it."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"金盈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"63138fecb291964278eac7cd51882c0b5c30f276","tid":870933,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a89a15fd52592a3dc8c237732a8e816dbfea8502","tid":870933,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0798f170488a4652f8c69380434200b695d9f385","tid":870933,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"Low likes it."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"金盈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:14:16.000Z","msg":"好撚煩呀你"},{"pid":"38aaf319b6bf6a13b2ff66080b406a9534e6de3c","tid":870933,"uid":61357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"應該用啲煙頭辣佢<br />\n再攞煙灰缸打佢個頭喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}